data.description: Spacious 4 Bedroom with 3 full Bathrooms! Entertainers Open floor plan Kitchen with prep island with modern sink and Granite countertops and walk in pantry, designers choice of modern laminate flooring throughout. Convenient bedroom and full bath downstairs. Choose from multiple relaxing areas from spacious formal living room ready for that projector type TV for the sports watching to cozying up in the family room next to the fireplace or choose quiet time in the third living room space in upstairs Loft. Home offers plenty of space for everyone! Relax in the Primary suite separate soak in tub and appreciate the space in your very own spacious primary closet with custom dual mirror doors. Super low maintenance modern Desert rock Landscaping in Front yard and No maintenance rear yard with Full side to side concrete slab ready for your patio furnishing to enjoy the cooling nights of the Desert. House is Move-In Ready. Come by check it out, must see to appreciate!
